Vanda Godsell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vanda_Godsell 0 Vanda Godsell (17 November 1922 – 11 April 1990) was an English actress. Hal Erickson writes in Allmovie, "Vanda Godsell specialised in playing disheveled housewives, busybody landladies and blowsy domestics." She appeared as Mrs. Weaver in This Sporting Life (1963), Mrs. Pitt in Bitter Harvest (1965), Mrs. Goodge in The Wrong Box (1967) Vanda_Godsell ( 17_November_1922 – 11_April_1990 ) was an_English_actress .
